            "title": "鰂魚涌 逸樺園 高曠大廳亮麗舒適",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"鰂魚涌 逸樺園 高曠大廳亮麗舒適\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b770b0cff7f586bd141160aed01cc922/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250321/_2025032113411725541.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">鰂魚涌 逸樺園 高曠大廳亮麗舒適</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>鰂魚涌社區配套發展完善，是用家及收租客置業熱門之選。今日為大家介紹逸樺園，鄰近港鐵太古站及電車站，市場現正有2房單位放盤，單位為2座極高層C室，實用面積616方呎，內櫳裝修企理，向正南，飽覽山景。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150454/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鰂魚涌逸樺園2座極高層C室，實用面積616方呎，現時月租叫價27500元。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14b287c0da9792ecc60ea51a49126840/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_23_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鰂魚涌逸樺園2座極高層C室，實用面積616方呎，現時月租叫價27500元。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150455/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"房間開則方正，面積寬敞闊落。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/777f7f7002b5832afe801a3cf836bbe1/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_24_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        房間開則方正，面積寬敞闊落。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150456/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"廚房設L形工作枱，保養相當新淨。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db92eb2de43593d5fe8cb92567640faf/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_24_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廚房設L形工作枱，保養相當新淨。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150457/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位向正南，享開揚市景及山景。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3197437110fe465317da5ca05c46d226/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-18_at_1_35_24_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位向正南，享開揚市景及山景。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4150460/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"逸樺園外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bd46d271ed4df1aab091980e2d9bdc8f/2025-03/DSCN9976.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        逸樺園外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>今日參觀的單位向正南，方向佳，擁有舒適的居住環境，走訪單位內櫳，見廳堂開則修長，樓底高，加上近落地玻璃設計，一廳高曠透亮。廳堂已附有雅緻裝潢，白色主調加上實木地板，再配襯不同色系家具，整體簡約素雅。廳堂設有近落地玻璃採光，外望翠綠山巒及康怡花園一帶樓景，視野開揚。放盤為2房間隔，房間皆方正實用，方便布置大牀及衣櫃等。浴室方面，備有光潔的浴具，設窗戶通風。\n\n</p>\n<p>逸樺園由太古地產發展，樓齡約22年，由2座組成，提供442個單位，間隔主要為2房及3房。此外，屋苑數分鐘步程即達港鐵太古站，附近也有商場康怡廣場，內有大型超級市場。\n\n</p><h2>放租單位資料</h2>\n<p>物業名稱：逸樺園\n\n</p>\n<p>地址 :鰂魚涌基利路3號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：22年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：2座極高層C室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：616方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：2房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫租：27500元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎租：45元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：利嘉閣地產\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：6461 6938（黃先生）\n\n</p>\n<p>*相片由代理提供\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
